SystemWindow subclass: #Window	instanceVariableNames: ''	classVariableNames: ''	package: 'ReflectiveWindow'!!Window commentStamp: 'ThomasWilkinson 10/27/2022 20:14' prior: 0!Class:  A window that is used to demonstrate reflectivity. Responsibility: Creates a window and inspects it. Provides methods alongside the inherited methods to edit the window at runtime. Collaborators: Subclass of SystemWindow. Creates a SimpleButtonMorph object. Public API and Key MessagesAdds a button which changes the window's label to the given value.Changes the window's colour. Changes the window's position. Changes the window's dimensions.!!Window methodsFor: 'initialization' stamp: 'ThomasWilkinson 10/30/2022 18:31'!initialize	super initialize.	self setLabel: 'Window'.	bounds := 0 @ 0 corner: 200 @ 200.	self beResizeable.	self openInWorld.	self inspect.			! !!Window methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'ThomasWilkinson 10/26/2022 18:02'!changeWidth: bound1 height: bound2	self width: bound1.	self height: bound2.! !!Window methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'ThomasWilkinson 10/26/2022 18:09'!changeColor: colour	self color: colour.! !!Window methodsFor: 'accessing' stamp: 'ThomasWilkinson 10/26/2022 18:24'!changePosition: pos1 y: pos2	| point |	point := Point new setX: pos1 setY: pos2.	self position: point.! !!Window methodsFor: 'adding' stamp: 'ThomasWilkinson 10/30/2022 18:52'!addLabelButton: string	| button |	button := SimpleButtonMorph new.	button label: 'Set Label'.	button target: self. 	button actionSelector: #setLabel:.	button arguments: (Array with: string).	button position: 5@30.	self addMorphFront: button.	button openInWindow.	! !